North Redwood.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...
- At 900 AM CDT Monday, the stage was 23.4 feet.
- River levels are falling.
- Forecast...The river is expected to fall to 22.1 feet Monday,
September 01.
- Flood stage is 21.0 feet.
- Flood History...This crest compares to a previous crest of
23.5 feet on 06/25/2013.</Snippet>
