   <Snippet>* WHAT...Northwest winds 5 to 15 kt with gusts up to 20 kt
expected.

* WHERE...Chesapeake Bay and adjoining estuaries north of Smith
Point VA, and Tidal Potomac from Cobb Island MD to Smith Point
VA.

